{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"他问我：‘你确是诚信的吗？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"难道我们死后，已变为尘土和朽骨的时候，还必定要受报酬吗？’”"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"他说：“你们愿看他吗？”"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"他俯视下面，就看见他在火狱的中央，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"他说：“以安拉发誓，你的确几乎陷害了我。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":57,"Text":"如果没有我的主的恩惠，我必在被拘禁者之列。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":58,"Text":"我们不是再死的吗？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":59,"Text":"唯有我们初次的死亡，而我们绝不会受惩罚吗？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":60,"Text":"这确是伟大的成功，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":61,"Text":"工作者应当为获得这样的成功而工作。”"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":62,"Text":"那是更善的款待呢？还是攒楛树？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":63,"Text":"我以它为不义者的折磨。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":64,"Text":"它是在火狱底生长的一棵树，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":65,"Text":"它的花篦，仿佛魔头。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":66,"Text":"他们必定要吃那些果实，而以它充实肚腹。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":67,"Text":"然后他们必定要在那些果实上加饮沸水的混汤，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":68,"Text":"然后他们必定归于火狱。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":69,"Text":"他们必定会发现他们的祖先是迷误的，"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":70,"Text":"他们却依着他们的踪迹而奔驰。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":71,"Text":"在他们之前，大半的古人确已迷误了。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":72,"Text":"我在他们之间，确已派遣过许多警告者。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":73,"Text":"你看！被警告者的结局是怎样的？"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":74,"Text":"除非安拉的纯洁的仆人们。"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":75,"Text":"努哈确已向我祈祷，我是最善于应答的！"},{"SurahNumber":37,"VerseNumber":76,"Text":"我拯救他和他的信徒们逃离大难。"}]}